    "Other models such as CNN (MSE = 0.42323), MLP (MSE = 0.29876), and LSTM (MSE = 0.37654) report higher error values.",
    "Among other existing models, BayesNet 15 recorded an MSE of 0.5121, Naive Bayes 16 had an MSE of 0.4794, SVM 23 reported an MSE of 0.4321 while ID3 + SVM 24 had an MSE of 0.469, which all have greater error margins showing how better DeepEnrollNet deals with errors.",
